# 行尾字节冻结：本仓 CRLF/LF 混居系历史事实，协作各端一律按仓储字节原样 checkout/commit。
# 字节保真高于风格统一——守恒审计、热更 diff、CJK 计数比对都依赖字节不变。
# 任何人不得开启 autocrlf 转换或做全仓行尾统一（会制造万行假 diff 并毁掉逐字节校验基线）。
* -text

# 明确二进制（防 diff/merge 误处理）
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.mp3 binary
*.ogg binary
*.wav binary
*.zip binary
*.apk binary
*.glb binary
*.gltf binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.pdf binary
*.save.json binary

# 本文件历史契约为 CRLF；仍检查真正的行尾空格，但不把 CR 本身误报为 trailing whitespace。
web/tm-endturn-prompt.js whitespace=blank-at-eol,blank-at-eof,space-before-tab,cr-at-eol

